⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Formless Mother
node ER · ER · ⟦The Formless Mother:ER:5abef5⟧

WHO   — The Formless Mother — the wound-loving god of blood
WHAT  — The Outer God of blood — a wounded, formless presence that craves wounds and offers accursed blood in return.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Outer Gods beyond the Lands Between; the blood beneath the earth  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Her element is blood itself, and through it she claims lords — Mohg pledged himself to her and dreamed a dynasty in her name.
HOW   — She gives as she takes — accursed blood for wounds, and from that blood a fire that curdles, bloodflame for the devoted.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  She has no form but the wound, and no gift but the blood that burns.

